  {
    "id": "ch_mndqkdkoruqwr",
    "text": "come work with me i can save you money on your 401k \n\nHere's what most people get wrong about market volatility:\n\nThey focus on the short-term noise instead of the long-term signal.\n\nThe data is clear. The math doesn't lie. And yet emotion wins every time.\n\nHere's how I help clients cut through it:\n\n1. Anchor to your plan, not the market\n2. Automate decisions before emotion can interfere\n3. Review quarterly — not daily\n\nWhat's your biggest challenge with market volatility?",
