  {
    "id": "ch_mndqkdkptzqjr",
    "text": "If you’re planning to take advantage of the new TRUMP Accounts for your children when they become available later this year, then here’s a quick update.\n\nThese accounts are designed to help families invest on behalf of children with tax advantages, encouraging long-term wealth building from an early age.\n\nKey highlights:\n• $1,000 government seed contribution for eligible children born between 2025–2028\n• Up to $5,000 per year in contributions from families, employers, or others\n• Investments limited to low-cost U.S. index funds\n• Funds generally accessible starting at age 18\n\nIf you or someone that you know is interested in setting one up for a newborn once they become available, let me know and they will be added to our contact list for updates.\n\n#FinancialPlanning #WealthBuilding #Investing #TRUMPAccounts",
