    "id": "ch_mndqkdkplsprm",
    "text": "Willl the market’s momentum from 2025 continue? How should you adjust your portfolio? What are 2026’s economic risks? In this next virtual client event, we’ll set the stage on what you can expect in the coming year. You won’t want to miss it!\n\nRegister Here: https://bit.ly/4pLrj0T",
